    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely slice <strong>half </strong>your <strong>red</strong> <strong>onion[s]</strong>, then finely dice the remaining</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lemongrass-and-sticky-onion-pork-burger-with-warm-sweet-potato-salad/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add<strong> </strong>the <strong>diced onion</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>rice vinegar</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong> and set aside to pickle \u2013 this is your <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lemongrass-and-sticky-onion-pork-burger-with-warm-sweet-potato-salad/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>mince</strong>, <strong>tomato paste </strong>and <strong>lemongrass & lime leaf paste </strong>to a bowl</p><p>Give everything a good mix up until thoroughly combined (clean hands are the best way!)</p><p>Shape into 1 patty per person</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lemongrass-and-sticky-onion-pork-burger-with-warm-sweet-potato-salad/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong>, once hot, add the <strong>patty[ies]</strong> and press down firmly with a spatula, add the <strong>sliced onion </strong>to the pan with a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and cook for 5 min on one side</p><p>After 5 min, reduce the heat to medium-high, flip the patty[ies] and cook for a further 5 min or until the patties are cooked through (no pink meat!) and the onions have softened</p><p>Once cooked, drizzle your <strong>soy sauce</strong> over your patty[ies] and onions and cook for 1 min further or until sticky</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lemongrass-and-sticky-onion-pork-burger-with-warm-sweet-potato-salad/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your <strong>potato[es]</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the<strong> chopped potatoes</strong> to a heatproof bowl, then cover the bowl with<strong> cling film</strong> and pierce a few holes in the top with a fork</p><p>Put the bowl in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 7-8 min or until the potatoes are fork-tender</p><p>Once the potatoes are tender add a knob of <strong>butter </strong>and a little <strong>salt </strong>to the bowl and stir it together<strong> </strong>\u2013 these are your <strong>buttery potatoes</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lemongrass-and-sticky-onion-pork-burger-with-warm-sweet-potato-salad/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong>, reserve the pickling liquid and save the bowl</p><p>Combine your <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw mix </strong>with the <strong>reserved pickling liquid </strong>in the reserved bowl and season with a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>tangy slaw</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lemongrass-and-sticky-onion-pork-burger-with-warm-sweet-potato-salad/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half and place in the <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lemongrass-and-sticky-onion-pork-burger-with-warm-sweet-potato-salad/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>To build your burger, divide the <strong>salad</strong> between the<strong> toasted ciabatta base[s] </strong>and top with the <strong>lemongrass patty</strong>, <strong>sticky onions </strong>and <strong>toasted ciabatta lid </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>lemongrass & sticky onion burger</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>tangy slaw </strong>and <strong>buttery potatoes</strong> topped with the <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
